    <item>
      <title>Hindenburg 与印度监管机构的争执加剧，Adani 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/adani-stocks-drop-as-hindenburg-row-with-india-regulator-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research) 指责印度首席市场监管机构存在利益冲突，阻碍对该企业集团欺诈指控进行彻底调查后，阿达尼集团的股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/adani-stocks-drop-as-hindenburg-row-with-india-regulator-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 04:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注伊朗报复，油价在周度上涨后保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价自 7 月初以来首次周线上涨后趋于稳定，市场仍在等待伊朗对上个月哈马斯领导人在德黑兰被暗杀事件作出回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
