      <title>套利交易崩盘令市场忧心忡忡，因​​仓位迅速缩减而陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/carry-trade-blowup-haunts-markets-rattled-by-rapid-fire-unwind</link>
